document_data.mainbody:
Marhymbel House Shipways was one of the best shipwright workshops in the Sea of Fallen Stars, based in Sarshel of Impiltur in 1490s DR.
By the late 15 century DR, Marhymbel House Shipways had been in business for two generations and was known as the fastest shipbuilders of rugged top-quality naval vessels that were reinforced for strength to weather any storm. Brother Ilund Marhymbel and Vromur Marhymbel were in charge for the Shipways.
